														<div class="source">
															</div>
							<div class="blogpost-content">
								<p><span style="color: rgb(112, 87, 75); font-size: 16px;">One of the most harmful thing that a person can choose to do to his or her body is to smoke tobacco. Why? Because tobacco use is the most common preventable cause of death in the United States. Despite this knowledge many smokers are not convinced that their addiction to tobacco is harmful. To make matters worse, many even believe that they can choose to break their bad habit whenever they want. The reality is that addiction to smoking can be very hard to break. There is no immediate danger from tobacco use because the dangerous chemicals in tobacco smoke take several years to manifest their ill consequences. This gives a false sense of security and when the ill effects are discovered it is often too late. If you commit to smoking cessation today, you may be able to improve the quality and quantity of your life and your loved onesâ€™ lives through the mechanisms below.</span><br></p>
